Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.45,0:00:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,關於淩晨發生於阿留多人街頭的炸彈恐怖事件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.93,0:00:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聯邦警察懷疑這次恐怖事件可能是針對前來阿留多人街進行慰問的\N同盟總領事兼和平特使貝·凱拉布·貝拉氏的暗殺行動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.80,0:00:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而持續調查中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說是恐怖事件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭  討厭  社會動亂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,問題已經很嚴重了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.36,0:00:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不能給同盟侵略中立地區的口實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同盟是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:43.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我們聯邦在銀河均等的勢力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.62,0:00:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在圍繞著貝利奧斯塔中立地區的所有權互相對立
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.51,0:00:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.37,0:00:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.58,0:00:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是恐怖事件發生前監視攝影機拍到的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是烏魯卡人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.53,0:01:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你能停留時間還有兩天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有得到更長的許可了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.99,0:01:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝您同意我參加調查
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.53,0:01:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這地方真可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:02:58.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由於炸彈恐怖事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:03:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿留多人街一帶被毀得一片狼藉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此現場還未能確認貝·凱拉布·貝拉氏的遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,生存的可能性近乎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,潘戈里安牛奶蘇打
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了緩和中立地區的緊張氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.57,0:03:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,德爾烏吉市市政官對同盟…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,12帕爾  先付錢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不便宜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這一帶同族很少見啊   多少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那位小哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣  博伊拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿留多的女人又臭又討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  那麼冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.77,0:03:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我技術很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咯吱  咯吱  咯吱  咯吱  咯吱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很熟練啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你昨天在阿留多街吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.39,0:03:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你知道的可真清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我對你一見鍾情了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  你為什麼會在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這可不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不要停  求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不告訴我就不幫你做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那  那個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.74,0:04:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是一般做生意的女人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這把槍是禁止一般人持有的貝諾加型光線槍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡把你作為現行犯逮捕要更省事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.37,0:04:47.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊  我們可是有營業執照的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.48,0:04:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他們要逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:04:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逃到這裡應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是攜帶違法槍支的現行犯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有你  還沒回答我的問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接著來享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:27.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畢多拉  救我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你下手還是不夠狠呐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.76,0:05:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奈丘拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧你做的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.81,0:05:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然不能殺掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要抓活的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  你做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放開  蠻力女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你才快給我住手  分屍狂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨  畢多拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.07,0:06:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幫我大忙了  尼姆凱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那時如果不是神祇官介入的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嫌疑犯就能抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼她會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神祇官直屬於奧之院  不受司法管制
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,加上她還是特察官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特撮片監督？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  是指獲得殺人許可的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.11,0:06:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而她介入了這次的調查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來奧之院對此事有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼樣  現在又回到起點了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話不能這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,數小時前  自稱新秩序革命戰線的組織發表了犯罪聲明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唯吉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喲  聯邦的諸位公僕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是還在浪費稅金啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好  我是新秩序革命戰線的司令官金澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是金澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  就是在艾爾卡扎姆被你和奈丘拉抓住的金澤爾·豪瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是米拉托綜合大學畢業的知識分子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在行星艾翁上做著吃人的野蠻行徑的兇惡恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,半年前  從阿特拉的衛星監獄逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我們再次警告諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,12小時後  給予那骯髒的同盟總領事館制裁之錘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是仁慈的我想給諸位最後的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.24,0:08:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能滿足我們的要求  可以取消這次正義行動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為此  我們指定這兩人來談判
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿嘿  看著吧  她倆馬上就要來談判了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我吃發臭牢飯的那些母貓們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我饒不了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:30.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對饒不了你們  那些臭婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乖  乖  乖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  一直給我們資金援助的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊  告訴我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.57,0:08:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是能夠理解我的革命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是大學裡的好伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這次的工作也是那位贊助者大人的委託
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,炸毀同盟的領事館對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:08:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是個幌子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.19,0:09:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說出來下你一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這次的目標是那些計算機人類的老窩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  那就是把奧之院…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然從大學出來的做事就是不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說這次的也是媲美反物質炸彈的煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:30.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,機動公安部那邊習慣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:33.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個年紀了還在實際行動部隊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.27,0:09:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是挺好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你適合跑現場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  貝利奧斯塔中立地區好像集結了同盟的艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會發展到戰爭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們正在盡力阻止啊  唯吉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.41,0:09:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為此  我們要儘快逮捕金澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作為同族真是感到丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:10:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是金澤爾是個二流主義者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們認為就憑他一個人能策劃出這次的計劃來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你發現什麼了嗎  斯凱爾茲奧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…說起來  那對搭檔重新組合了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:14.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼又是跟你這傢伙合作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還包括金澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,金澤爾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能我們之間有緣分的紅線連著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你開玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這人還會開玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是來自這裡的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從懂事的時候開始  都是白奧林在照顧我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,育兒用機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  母親的替代品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奧林？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:10:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們阿留多人的公墓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,金澤爾  按照約定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪·希馮以及另一人來談判了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這情況原來也遇到過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和艾爾卡扎姆是一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:25.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是沒進步的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到沒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這慘狀  活不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是  嘿嘿  真是活該
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:51.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼  阿留多人的小鬼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼處理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們被他看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:11:58.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,解決掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他還是個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了  親愛的  別殺他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在工作完成之前  把他關起來怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.03,0:12:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,切  知道啦  隨你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到你就是贊助者大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你裝死真是把我都嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凱拉布總領事殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別廢話了  金澤爾·豪瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,汝只要完成餘的委託就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.97,0:13:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首都上空1萬繆魯的靜止衛星軌道上漂浮的廢棄電力衛星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把這衛星落到奧之院上去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣讓半徑40繆魯毀滅的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,衛星下降開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在高度8千  進入角度70  誤差修正25比塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:51.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按預定路線下降中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦  該怎麼做才好  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話  現在停止也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.79,0:14:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為一按這個衛星就會自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,金澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈  開玩笑  玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同盟的傢伙們不懂幽默還真是沒轍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:14.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功  那個是控制器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:15.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以奧之院毀滅為信號
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們艦隊向中立地區的中心進軍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.28,0:14:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以壓倒的戰力光復曾今失去的領土
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作為和平特使的余被聯邦暗殺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如有這個大義名分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的進攻就是正當的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了的和平特使
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小男孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這小鬼  站住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.73,0:14:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把那東西還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:14:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老實待著  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就把你生吞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛  你能辦得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.21,0:15:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,認命吧  金澤爾·豪瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然招來了搜查官  金澤爾這個白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖分子的老巢裡出現了本該死去的同盟總領事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.56,0:15:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣的組合
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,金澤爾  你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大吃一驚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大學裡我製造的傑作三重阿努比斯7
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有匹敵重型戰車的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別人說話要聽完
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,0:16:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,該死的金澤爾  竟然讓衛星墜落…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,墜落地點分析完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目標是奧之院
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用  沒用  沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,它比你們調整型阿留多人更強大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.63,0:16:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別小看大學生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:21.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:27.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叫你把我的話聽完
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,親愛的  這個怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尼姆凱  快交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.83,0:16:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}距離目標還有60
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說  那個要是墜落了  很多無辜的人會喪命的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:17:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  大概50人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別聽這女人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還要多得多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會死很多人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我愛你  我的甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾  就差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您說的話我不太明白  神祇官殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「以奧之院毀滅為信號
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.66,0:17:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們艦隊向中立地區的中心進軍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以壓倒的戰力光復曾今失去的領土」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:45.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.36,0:17:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個公佈出去的話  同盟就…啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊  神祇官出現在這裡是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你能明白  我們也省事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.85,0:18:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是本國同盟政府的意圖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,閣下充滿勇氣的行為將給我們雙方帶來利益
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,處世之道我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以吾之血為同盟正義的標誌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,政治了結嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:24.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.27,0:18:27.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.20,0:18:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡  竟會在這裡  我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  那隻野狗在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是大學畢業的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:18:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你的功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,金澤爾及其同伙被阿特拉的衛星收容所監禁了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同盟也接受凱拉布總領事因為恐怖分子而殉職的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.09,0:19:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,撤回指責
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.69,0:19:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,避免了一觸即發的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是所謂的政治了結
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候我失去知覺沒法聯絡你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是怎麼確定他們的老巢的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這問題由我來回答
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.07,0:19:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是你！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我來介紹  他是潛入搜查官…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡修·蓋澤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他也是斯凱爾茲奧的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我原來也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.98,0:19:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是秘密作戰  請原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是斯凱爾茲奧教官的弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.27,0:19:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是你的同門
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.83,0:19:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,潛入調查的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最初的恐怖事件也可以防患於未然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不那麼做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就無法揭穿同盟的陰謀了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  巴迪  住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就原諒他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他是為了完成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜犧牲無辜的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是為了拯救更多的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是為了拯救更多的生命嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈  我不配說這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說軍方的工作人員也潛入了
